s://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","JSXOpeningElement","no-unused-vars","'isDarkMode' is assigned a value but never used.","Identifier","unusedVar","'setSearchTerm' is assigned a value but never used.","'isOverlayOpen' is assigned a value but never used.","'isHovered' is assigned a value but never used.","'setIsHovered' is assigned a value but never used."]